title: Bloomberg Markets: Joseph on `Winning' Documentary

description:
Bloomberg Markets with Carol Massar and Cory Johnson.\u0010\u0010GUEST:\u0010Jacqueline Joseph\u0010Documentary Filmmaker\u0010JJ Unlimited Productions\u0010Discussing her documentary "Winning" the compelling and inspiring story of the journeys of Nadia Comaneci, Edwin Moses, Martina Navratilova, Jack Nicklaus and Paralympian tennis champion Esther Vergeer.
